Johannesburg - Katy Perry has announced that she will be performing in South Africa for the very first time as part of WITNESS: The Tour. The US singer will be performing in Johannesburg on 18 and 20 July 2018 at the Ticketpro Dome. Tickets go on sale at 9am on 26 January 2018 via www.bigconcerts.co.za. Discovery Card holders get an exclusive 48-hour pre-sale from 24th January 2018 at 9am. Go to www.discovery.co.za for more information. Perry announced her visit to Joburg in a YouTube video:   WITNESS: the Tour is described as "an imaginative trip from outer-space to inner-space, from the planets to the bottom of our oceans, and a musical journey through Katy Perry’s biggest milestones and mega-hits right up to her latest album. "The dramatically original staging means that there isn’t a bad seat in the house, when Katy brings out her band and dancers, along with all the bells and whistles." IOL